casebody.head_matter:
Jesse G. YATES, III, et ux., petitioners,
v.
COMMISSIONER OF INTERNAL REVENUE.
No. 13-8745.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 31, 2014.
Motion of petitioners for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioners allowed until April 21, 2014, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
